The key was turned, the gates were opened wide
St Peter and woman walked inside and there
within the sunshine of the throne,
She saw the little Garden she had grown
1939-2010"¤
╠WAYNE Energy ALLEYNE
SUNRSE 8 DECEMBER 1967 - 2  OCTOBER 2010 SUNSET
IN LOVING MEMORY
MY HUSBAND FATHER SON BROTHER UNCLE FRIEND
8
ÔÇťDANCE LIKE THERE'S NO BODY WATCHINGÔÇŁ
AND I WILL DANCE WITH YOU"ď
ĐTo our baby girl
OLIVIA "GASINETTICA" LANDRIAU SARACENT
Who was born sleeping on the 19th of June 2016 at 2.08am
"Out beyond ideas of right and wrong, there is a field
We will meet you there."
Mami & Papa"ˇ
